text: ==Notes== Theodore Thomas More Agnew, Baron Agnew of Oulton, DL is a British businessman, Conservative life peer, and former Minister of State at the Cabinet Office and HM Treasury. He is the founder and current chairman of the board of Inspiration Trust, an academy trust in Norfolk and Suffolk. ==Notes== ==Other websites== Category:Living people Category:1961 births Category:British businesspeople Category:Conservative members of the House of Lords
